expression.simple_expression:
"

Model for a VAV terminal box with a water reheat coil and exponential damper.

"

"
  • January 27, 2023, by Jianjun Hu:
    Changed the pressure independent damper to exponential damper. This is for issue #3139.
  • December 20, 2021, by Michael Wetter:
    Changed parameter declarations for issue #2829.
  • August 24, 2021, by Michael Wetter:
    Changed model to include the hydraulic configurations of the cooling coil, heating coil and VAV terminal box.
    This is for issue #2594.
  • February 12, 2021, by Baptiste Ravache:
    First implementation, based on Buildings.Obsolete.Examples.VAVReheat.BaseClasses.VAVBranch
    This is for #2024.
"
